column5: For the first few months of the 'BRAGGIN' RIGHTS' fishing tourney, there was LOTS of interest . . .    new entries almost EVERY day, but by mid-summer it was seldom being mentioned . . . . .    by fall . . . .    NOODNIK? Is there gonna be 'official standings' posted, or have they already been on the main board? There seemed to be a huge bunch registered . . . .     how did everyone make out? Who was the over-all whiner . . . .   er r r r  r . . . . .     WINNER?
